<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka vakvaih na gam thip gamdai hi chu,
 Dah a um nalawm lawm sek na e!
 Khenna ni leh dak atung hi,
 Ka guol leh ka pai ngaih haw hi.

[V2]
 Ana na e maw! Aw ka Lal nunnem,
 Thagau thiengtho in hung inla;
 Na hungtun kal ka ngak lah ui,
 Ka gam uh lungsiet um sungah.

[V3]
 2. Zie malgam tangpi thavai chung ahin,
 Na tha zakin Lal Immanuel;
 Tatsa dawng ngikngiek hawcha hi,
 Aw ka Lal nunnem hung entan.

[V4]
 3. Tuonna ei suonte Evi leh Adam
 Lalpa'n a guot Eden huon thiengah,
 Eden huon hawih tuola lenglai
 Aw ka Lal nunnem na chan maw!

[V5]
 4. Aw Lalpa Pathien leh thagau thienglim
 Eden hehpihna huih a nun lai hin
 Thisan paktan a lenghaw chung,
 Thepna meipi hun hawk kieng ta'n.</lyrics>
<title>Ka Vak Vaihna Gamthip</title>
<author>Lienrum</author>
<hymn_number>253</hymn_number>
</song>